              "id" : "2-ether-land",
              "paras" : [ "The shuttle drops onto its landing gear and, immediately, alarms and damage reports slam into your mind. Entire sections of the shipyard have been destroyed.", "$cv:pc_player{the base's ether network is still online} You and Karengo reach the conclusion at the same time." ],
